@startuml
!pragma layout smetana

title Exit Command Sequence Diagram

actor User
participant Resumake
participant Parser
participant ExitCommand
participant Ui
participant Storage

User -> Resumake: bye
Resumake -> Parser: parse(input, ui)
Parser --> Resumake: ExitCommand
Resumake -> ExitCommand: execute(list)
ExitCommand -> Ui: print bye
Resumake -> Storage: saveToFile(list)
Storage -> Storage: serialize + compare + skip if unchanged
Resumake -> Resumake: isExit = true
@enduml
